Stand up, Jaden.
Come on. Get up.

107
00:10:06,340 --> 00:10:07,741
Thanks, guys.

108
00:10:09,710 --> 00:10:11,145
Hey,

109
00:10:11,178 --> 00:10:13,380
you became a man in here, okay?

110
00:10:23,824 --> 00:10:25,993
[grunting, groaning]

111
00:10:28,896 --> 00:10:30,064
Fuck.

