two minutes here.

124
00:11:10,938 --> 00:11:11,972
Come on.

125
00:11:28,322 --> 00:11:30,691
All right, finally.

126
00:11:35,262 --> 00:11:36,297
[chuckles]

127
00:11:38,999 --> 00:11:40,034
