134
00:12:03,558 --> 00:12:06,827
[thuds] Geez, the Holy Ghost.

135
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:08,462
[laughs]
[Rhodes] How's it going, Father?

136
00:12:08,495 --> 00:12:11,065
