brother.

158
00:13:59,641 --> 00:14:01,008
[sighs]

159
00:14:02,510 --> 00:14:03,944
I've been right where you are.

160
00:14:05,346 --> 00:14:07,948
They tossed me in jail
and threw away the key.

161
00:14:11,653 --> 00:14:12,920
All that pain.

162
